{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"關鍵詞","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Keyword","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>關鍵詞</strong>是描述内容的字或短語。在綫關鍵詞被用於搜索引擎的查詢或用來識別站點上的内容.</p>\n<p>當你使用搜索引擎，你會使用指定的關鍵詞來搜索你想查找的東西，搜索引擎根據關鍵詞來返回相關的結果頁。爲了搜索到更精準的結果，需要嘗試更多指定的關鍵詞，如使用 \"Blue Mustang GTO\" 代替簡單的 \"Mustang\"。網頁也可以用 meta 標簽(寫在 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/head\"><code>&lt;head&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>使用關鍵詞描述頁面的内容，它可以使搜索引擎更好的定義和組織網頁。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基礎知識","title":"基礎知識","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>維基百科上的 <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Keyword_research\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">關鍵詞</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"關鍵詞是描述内容的字或短語。在綫關鍵詞被用於搜索引擎的查詢或用來識別站點上的内容.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Keyword","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Palabra clave","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Mot-clé","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Keyword (キーワード)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Palavra-chave","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Keyword","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/glossary/keyword","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/glossary/keyword/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary","title":"術語表"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Keyword","title":"關鍵詞"}],"pageTitle":"關鍵詞 - 術語表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}